snippet.title: NoClueGaming
snippet.description: Just two gals who have no clue what they are doing. All that matters is getting the game, playing the game, beating the game and hopefully not getting lost and falling into a deep depression after they realize their life is a scam and they have no friends or life because they never left the house to experience what the world is and now they are forever alone with nothing to do but play games until they die : forgot to mention, we are immortal. I have no clue why I wrote that but anyways, welcome to NoClueGaming!
